  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello everyone! I am liangxie, the author of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"My Rose\" is a pixel-style precision platform jumping game. A boy sets out to find the soul fruit to save a girl. Will he be able to collect the soul fruit smoothly? And in the end, can he save the girl?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.poster.avif?t=1743998571\" width=468 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.webm?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.mp4?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game mainly includes more than 60 carefully designed levels, 4 protagonist abilities <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/c6e20016a418a4f12639b592df893c10.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/5441e5badf3f34231eb356d610364fda.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/4577a7835121825f5c558d2816c1b663.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/112386a916419b6468adb64f6958dcd9.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span>, 2 kinds of traps <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/594e6194e898a538fde2140e429aa1dd.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/68bcb2cd0a90b5669c94a5628bb475b3.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span> and a simple story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/78ecaef0093c7ca733d9a58f4e8d7e7f.poster.avif?t=1743998571\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/78ecaef0093c7ca733d9a58f4e8d7e7f.webm?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/78ecaef0093c7ca733d9a58f4e8d7e7f.mp4?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay that combines difficulty and ease and is diverse can allow everyone to get into the state from the very beginning. Through continuous attempts, they can break through layer by layer, advance the game, and obtain a dual experience of relaxation and excitement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game clearance time is about 1 to 2 hours. In addition to clearance <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/04df5872dfab16c07b9cfb7ac25cd036.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span>, three additional challenges <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/a4eb68c383cd2de97240f9d3aa455088.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/97a4d94ebb62feaa7b0f0baef0140f59.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/f14fc19da71165515a2c97a7c04f6300.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span> are set up, filling up the sense of achievement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/3dd73eb12b4cb196842c33cc88b52e44.poster.avif?t=1743998571\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/3dd73eb12b4cb196842c33cc88b52e44.webm?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/3dd73eb12b4cb196842c33cc88b52e44.mp4?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"My Rose\" is the author's first truly independent game. The game design, programming, art, and some music and sound effects are all completed by the author alone. I hope you will like this work. I also hope that everything in this world will have a beautiful ending.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello everyone! I am liangxie, the author of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"My Rose\" is a pixel-style precision platform jumping game. A boy sets out to find the soul fruit to save a girl. Will he be able to collect the soul fruit smoothly? And in the end, can he save the girl?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.poster.avif?t=1743998571\" width=468 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.webm?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.mp4?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game mainly includes more than 60 carefully designed levels, 4 protagonist abilities <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/c6e20016a418a4f12639b592df893c10.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/5441e5badf3f34231eb356d610364fda.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/4577a7835121825f5c558d2816c1b663.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/112386a916419b6468adb64f6958dcd9.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=